_sText:
This map is an AIM texture style mod of the original de_deathcookin. The main structure of the map is entirely down to the original authors, however, modifications to the map structure include:

3 New secret rooms and sniper holes hidden behind destructible walls
New routes to get from one side of the map to the other
All original models replaced with AIM Textured blocks to keep the theme
Lots of small area changes
